Description: Up for sale here is a 2001 Jackson DR3 Electric Guitar. This guitar is made in Japan and plays great. The color is translucent green with a black back. This guitar originally had duncan designed direct mount to body pickups. I changed the pickups to actual seymour duncan pickups (a jb in the bridge and a 59 in the neck). I added pickup mounting rings to be able to change pickups since the original duncan designed screw holes are much larger. There is nothing wrong with this guitar at all, I just don't play it. I have too many guitars and don't need this. It's a very nice guitar and I'd hate to see it just sit. It has some dings here and from regular wear but everything on this guitar works perfectly. I am including a padded gig bag, trem bar, as well as both floyd rose allen keys and the truss rod wrench that did not originally come with this guitar. Shipping is $50. I only accept regular paypal payments. NO E-CHECKS!!!!. This is a U.S. only auction. No international bids. I am not shipping this internationally. Buyers bid with confidence. I have 100% POSITIVE FEEDBACK and have been selling on ebay for well over a decade. If you have any questions please ask them before placing any bids. Thank you.
